    • precedingDataSet

      public String precedingDataSet
      Contains an identifier of the preceding process data set from which this process was derived. In case of a data set imported from an EcoSpold 2 file this could be the original activity ID for example (which is not unique between different data sets in ecoinvent) for example. Also, there is a corresponding field in the ILCD data exchange format.
